headline: Edwards Lifesciences (NYSE:EW) Projects 2025 Sales Over US$5.7 Billion With Strong Earnings
summary: Edwards Lifesciences (NYSE:EW) recently announced its updated guidance, projecting second-quarter 2025 sales between $1.45 billion and $1.53 billion, alongside first-quarter results showing a rise in sales and net income compared to the previous year. This aligns with a broader market trend where the S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite surged, driven by positive earnings reports and easing concerns over tariffs.
